    "name": "警察模拟器：巡警 - 高速巡警扩展包",
    "steam_appid": 2350410,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350410/extras/73f0c97d75f8614614ea9b4e57c5a9b8.poster.avif?t=1768874604\" width=620 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350410/extras/73f0c97d75f8614614ea9b4e57c5a9b8.webm?t=1768874604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">探索 Police Simulator: Patrol Officers扩展包，并拓展你的巡逻区域！探索各式各样的环境和更广大的Franklin州景色，同时进行刺激的公路追逐、快速部署PIT机动战术来策略性地阻止违规嫌犯逃脱，并享受更动态的警察模拟体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350410/extras/de6f683dc9b0934cf15adc8df493eb6c.poster.avif?t=1768874604\" width=620 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350410/extras/de6f683dc9b0934cf15adc8df493eb6c.webm?t=1768874604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">连接Brighton和Franklin州的公路因为一场重大交通事故而关闭了很长一段时间，且需要大面积重建。Brighton市长现在很高兴地宣布，他们举行了盛大的重新启用仪式。Brighton警察局及其警官现在可以在公路上巡逻，且获得了新的指派工作、新的挑战任务和责任，与新的工具，例如请求以钉刺带和路障来阻止劫车者逃脱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350410/extras/f75e776c36000bcd646edddf53d40dff.poster.avif?t=1768874604\" width=620 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350410/extras/f75e776c36000bcd646edddf53d40dff.webm?t=1768874604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">由于公路已重新启用，汽车盗窃的风险可能会提高，也会有更多事故涉及货车、火灾和散落货物。你的日常职责会增加，包括监控超速者、为受困驾驶员提供协助，以及检查货车中是否有非法物品。总而言之，你必须负责增加公路的安全。公路扩展包也会包含新的州际警车，可让玩家飒爽巡逻公路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350410/extras/9b0a715575e79c81950ab314448d4efa.poster.avif?t=1768874604\" width=620 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350410/extras/9b0a715575e79c81950ab314448d4efa.webm?t=1768874604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全新巡逻区域：Brighton公路地区</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全新功能：公路追逐、策略战术和更多内容</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全新任务：新的行动，例如货物检查和公路救援</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全新责任：管理并提升公路交通安全</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >新的违规：例如汽车盗窃、重大公路事故和更多内容</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全新工具：例如钉刺带和路障</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全新车辆：州际警车</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全新车辆：Endurance Police Vehicle</p></li></ul>",
